of income would be exporting.

58:50.652 --> 58:51.819
Oh.

58:51.820 --> 58:54.280
I have to go to the
little girls' room.

58:54.281 --> 58:56.524
Excuse me.

59:13.759 --> 59:17.136
I think we should move in together.

59:17.137 --> 59:21.632
- You're kidding, right?
- Do I sound like I'm kidding?

59:22.476 --> 59:26.387
- I can't move in with you, David.
- Why not?

59:29.316 --> 59:31.484
I don't approve of your lifestyle.

59:31.485 --> 59:33.611
