59:33.612 --> 59:36.322
when you were snorting up
everything I put in front of you.

59:36.323 --> 59:39.992
- You're missing the point.
- Check it.

59:39.993 --> 59:42.536
I got like 150 grand saved up.

59:42.537 --> 59:45.498
