01:00:02.349 --> 01:00:08.679
Aw, did I hurt your feelings? Look,
I'm just trying to be honest with you.

01:00:10.023 --> 01:00:12.692
Baby, look at me.

01:00:12.693 --> 01:00:14.735
Look at me.

01:00:14.736 --> 01:00:17.188
Now, I like partying with you.

01:00:17.197 --> 01:00:19.907
And I love fucking you.

01:00:19.908 --> 01:00:21.867
But that's where it ends.

01:00:21.868 --> 01:00:24.954
Now, why turn it into
something that it's not?

01:00:24.955 --> 01:00:29.333
Let's just have fun while it lasts.

01:00:29.334 --> 01:00:32.036
OK?

01:00:37.092 --> 01:00:40.761
Yeah, we'll do that.
While it lasts.

01:00:40.762 --> 01:00:44.256
She had me wrapped around her
little finger and she knew it.

01:00:44.349 --> 01:00:47.685
I used to laugh when I heard
niggas talk about being in love.

01:00:47.686 --> 01:00:50.271
Even writing the word
makes me feel helpless.

01:00:50.272 --> 01:00:51.814
But it's true.

01:00:51.815 --> 01:00:56.110
I'd never felt this way about another
person in my life, except my mother.

01:00:56.111 --> 01:01:00.573
And I didn't like it. I mean this
from the bottom of my heart.

01:01:00.574 --> 01:01:03.784
I hated this feeling
that I had for Juanita.

01:01:03.785 --> 01:01:08.414
It made me feel like I was...
Like I was weak.

01:01:11.209 --> 01:01:14.411
And we couldn't have that.

01:01:22.929 --> 01:01:26.140
They say revenge is a
dish best served cold.

01:01:26.141 --> 01:01:29.518
I was about to take my shit right
out the motherfucking freezer.

01:01:29.519 --> 01:01:31.729
Bitch thought she was
gonna get by without me,

01:01:31.730 --> 01:01:34.473
she'd be thinking again real soon.

01:01:35.817 --> 01:01:38.778
Might as well call me
a broken-down trick.

01:01:38.779 --> 01:01:42.448
Using me for my money and telling
me a quarter mil ain't good enough?

01:01:42.449 --> 01:01:44.492
A quarter mil's always good.

01:01:44.493 --> 01:01:52.493
It was good then and it
sure in hell's still good now.

01:02:01.843 --> 01:02:04.628
Still good now... Still good now...

01:02:16.441 --> 01:02:19.652
- Don't shoot. I'll give you...
- Shut up. All I need is a ride.

01:02:19.653 --> 01:02:21.895
Get in.

01:03:42.652 --> 01:03:44.937
Just keep driving.

01:03:49.659 --> 01:03:53.487
Whoa, stop the car,
stop the car. Back up.

01:03:55.457 --> 01:03:57.741
Slowly.

01:04:01.922 --> 01:04:04.915
Right here, right here, right here.

01:04:39.543 --> 01:04:41.544
Why was the tiger scared?

01:04:41.545 --> 01:04:44.380
- Why?
- It was rated Rrrr.

01:04:44.381 --> 01:04:47.383
- That's some funny shit.
- Oh, yeah.

01:04:47.384 --> 01:04:49.668
Come here.

01:04:50.720 --> 01:04:52.555
Uh-uh.

01:04:52.556 --> 01:04:55.182
