- Thank you, Daddy.

01:04:55.183 --> 01:04:59.303
That's right, baby. Now
give your sister some.

01:05:00.480 --> 01:05:03.190
Come on, baby.

01:05:03.191 --> 01:05:06.151
But don't drop it. What the fuck...

01:05:06.152 --> 01:05:08.445
What the fuck did
